data.description: Great home in Bridgewater subdivision, zoned for Nevils and Brooklet schools. Over 2500 square feet with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms plus a bonus room. Ample closet space throughout the entire house. Downstairs has a formal dining room, great room, kitchen with breakfast area, pantry, plus the master bedroom with 2 closets, half bath and laundry room. Upstairs has a bonus room with a closet, 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Fresh, neutral paint throughout. One year home warranty included for the buyer. Call today to view this home.
